org.jacop.search.sgmpcs

Class SGMPCSearch

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jacop.search.sgmpcs.SGMPCSearch

  • public class SGMPCSearch
extends Object
    SGMPCSearch - implements Solution-Guided Multi-Point Constructive Search. This search starts with several elite solutions and tries to impove (minimizing cost variable) them by doing either search assuming an elite solution or staring with an empty solution.

    This implementation is based on paper "Solution-guided Multi-point Constructive Search for Job Shop Scheduling" by J. Christopher Beck, Journal of Artificial Intelligence Research 29 (2007) 49â€“77.

    Version:
    4.7
    Author:
    Krzysztof Kuchcinski
